            "title": "〈熱門股〉全福4項眼科新藥專案穩健推進 單周狂漲逾4成",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>全福生技 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6885:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6885\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6885-TW</a>) 旗下 4 項眼科新藥，包含 BRM421、BRM424、BRM411 與 BRM412 開發專案持續穩健推進，BRM421 預計下半年提交第二次三期臨床申請，其他 3 項新藥今年也將進行二期臨床試驗，激勵全福本周大漲超過 4 成。 </p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011326%2Fl%2Ff17af478043c33baaabd66b38c5fbb54.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011326%2Fl%2Ff17af478043c33baaabd66b38c5fbb54.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011326%2Fl%2Ff17af478043c33baaabd66b38c5fbb54.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011326%2Fl%2Ff17af478043c33baaabd66b38c5fbb54.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011326%2Fl%2Ff17af478043c33baaabd66b38c5fbb54.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011326%2Fl%2Ff17af478043c33baaabd66b38c5fbb54.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011326%2Fl%2Ff17af478043c33baaabd66b38c5fbb54.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011326%2Fl%2Ff17af478043c33baaabd66b38c5fbb54.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011326%2Fl%2Ff17af478043c33baaabd66b38c5fbb54.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011326%2Fl%2Ff17af478043c33baaabd66b38c5fbb54.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011326%2Fl%2Ff17af478043c33baaabd66b38c5fbb54.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011326%2Fl%2Ff17af478043c33baaabd66b38c5fbb54.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011326%2Fl%2Ff17af478043c33baaabd66b38c5fbb54.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011326%2Fl%2Ff17af478043c33baaabd66b38c5fbb54.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011326%2Fl%2Ff17af478043c33baaabd66b38c5fbb54.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011326%2Fl%2Ff17af478043c33baaabd66b38c5fbb54.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011326%2Fl%2Ff17af478043c33baaabd66b38c5fbb54.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">全福4項眼科新藥專案穩健推進，周漲逾4成。(圖：shutterstock)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>全福本周漲勢凌厲，大漲 44.62%，周二 (3 日) 至周四 (5 日) 喜迎 3 根漲停，周五 (6 日) 收 32.9 元，除站回 30 元關卡，也一舉攻上半年線。不過三大法人周三至週五連續 3 個交易日賣超，本周合計賣超 488 張。 </p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>全福指出，旗下治療乾眼症新藥 BRM421 已完成全新配方與濃度優化，也於 5 月美國 FDA 提交劑量效應人體試驗臨床申請，預計下半年提交第二次三期臨床申請。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>至於其他 3 項眼科新藥，治療罕病神經營養性角膜炎 (NK) 的 BRM424 預計 6 月啟動臨床二期；青光眼新藥 BRM411 已向台灣 TFDA 提出第 I/IIb 人體臨床試驗 (IND) 申請，預計下半年進行臨床 IIb；治療濕式黃斑部病變的 BRM412，預計下半年向美國 FDA 提出諮詢會議後，送件臨床二期試驗開發。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>不過全福遭證交所列為警示股，公告 4 月自結損益，4 月營收 3.4 萬元，稅後虧損 3957 萬元，每股虧損 0.3 元。此外，全福也公告 5 月營收，114 萬元，月增 32.53 倍，累計今年前 5 月營收 127.4 萬元。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><figure><img data-cnyeschart=\"cnyeschart\" src=\"https://so.cnyes.com/mobilechart/MobileChart.aspx?markettype=twstock&amp;charttype1=kchart&amp;stockcode=6885&amp;imgwidth=580&amp;imgheight=500&amp;bgcolor=2\"/>\n<figcaption> </figcaption>\n</figure></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p> </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
